name: LFG-42 Scrambler Tank 01
description:
A brand new urban assault vessel featuring quad cannons with ballistic, incendiary, corrosive liquid and floral launching capabilities.

Holders of this Tank will receive weathered variants as it traverses the city, and also be entered to win editions of the concept art series, Scrambler City Nights.

Created by @alexdelia for Artifact.Quest
2021.
